############################################################
MAKING a Package
############################################################

Packaging:
-----------

1. update versions in debian/control
   (so that apt-get update sophomorix2 updates all sophomorix-* packages)

2. update date of release in changelog-sophomorix-src

3. cd cvs/sophomorix2

4. dch -i 
   add a comment to the changelog

5. make deb  (old: dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot)

6. Tag all files in the cvs repository with the tag 'Version-x-y-z'


Testing:
----------

1. install sophomorix-developer

2. Tests
   A) sophomorix-test
   B) sophomorix-test-bunchofusers --add
   C) sophomorix-test-bunchofusers --wsadd

   sophomorix-repair --permissions
   sophomorix-repair --repairhome
 
   D) sophomorix-test-bunchofusers --handout
   E) sophomorix-test-bunchofusers --collect
   F) sophomorix-test-bunchofusers --handoutcopy

3. No test is allowed to throw an error.






